      public FYP(int projectId, String supervisorName, String supervisorEmail, String studentID, String studentName, String studentEmail, String projectTitle, FYPStatus status)
      FYP represents a Final Year Project with its respective attributes.
      Parameters:
      projectId - the ID of the project.
      supervisorName - the name of the project supervisor.
      supervisorEmail - the email of the project supervisor.
      studentID - the ID of the student who is registered in this project.
      studentName - the name of the student who is registered in this project.
      studentEmail - the email of the student who is registered in this project.
      projectTitle - the title of the project.
      status - the status of the project.
